rComments: she is an amazing prof! she makes all lectures intersting. Best prof i've ever had so far and I would definitely take class with her again
She is very funny and I like that she's quirky. If you pay attention in class and do your readings you can easily get perfect.

Prof Shantz is great! She makes theories interesting, lectures are fun. She shows lots of great movies/videos which make class fun. She has group in-class assignments, easy marks! Also, no midterm/exams. Instead, she gives 2 midterm take-home papers and 1 final take-home paper. She's a really tough grader though, makes you work for a good grade.
Probably one of the best profs at UOttawa. Expectations are clear, assignments are fair and so is marking. Her style of teaching is SUPERB !!! Please give her more classes to teach !

Professor Shantz is a beaut! Super funny and shows modern day examples including her love for videos. Group assignments forth 30% ummm yes please! and she marks them super easy. Highly recommend taking her!

Laura is an amazing person! She is 100% there for her students, very easy to approach and engage in conversation. As someone who has gone through over 6 years of university, she THE most student friendly professor. Interesting lectures, loves group discussions, lets you talk and have your own opinion without throwing her own in your face. love!

Laura is one the best part-time professors at the UofO. She cares about her students and really engages the audience. She wants everyone to succeed by using practical examples to understand criminological theories. Take her for any course and you will enjoy it. Exams, readings, and take-home is all reasonable and easy if you attend class!
